			message: '#^PHPDoc type class\-string\<Illuminate\\Database\\Eloquent\\Model\> of property Database\\Factories\\InventoryItemFactory\:\:\$model is not covariant with PHPDoc type class\-string\<App\\Models\\InventoryItem\> of overridden property Illuminate\\Database\\Eloquent\\Factories\\Factory\<App\\Models\\InventoryItem\>\:\:\$model\.$#'
